Package suncertify.panels

This package contains various GUI panels and widgets used in the URLyBird client and server.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
FieldInputComponent Identifies a GUI component for entering a database field value for searching.
 

Class Summary
AbstractInputDialog A modal dialog box that dynamically enables and disables the OK button depending on the value entered by the user.
BooleanEntryField Our standard search field widget for booleans: an uneditable combo box.
FileOpenDialog A dialog box for entering a filename.
GenericEntryField Our standard input widget for search text: an editable combo box that performs some predictive completion as the user types.
HelpAboutPanel A simple "about" dialog box showing information about the program.
ModifyRecordPanel A dialog box that enables the user to modify a record.
ProgressDialog This class provides a simple dialog box that contains a progress bar and a cancel button.
RMIAddressDialog A dialog box for entering an RMI network address (or host name).
RMIAddressDocumentFilter Simple class to prevent invalid RMI address characters from being entered.
StringEntryField Our standard input widget for string search fields: an editable combo box that shows a list of matching items as the user types.
 

Package suncertify.panels Description

This package contains various GUI panels and widgets used in the URLyBird client and server.
